results.name: Number of ordered octuples of distinct pairwise coprime positive integers with largest element n.
link: Alois P. Heinz, Table of n, a(n) for n = 17..200
example: a(20) = 2 because there are 2 ordered octuples of distinct pairwise coprime positive integers with largest element 20: (1,3,7,11,13,17,19,20), (1,7,9,11,13,17,19,20).
